<!-- Book Section - Top Level -->
<div class="row">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="col-md-12 back-link">
      <a href="#" class="collation-back-link">
        <i class="fa fa-arrow-left" aria-hidden="true"></i>Back to pack creator</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="collation-table">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Download The Pack -->

      <div class="collation-table-cell">
        <div class="collation-icon">
          <img src="data:image/png;base64," width="71px" height="88px" alt="Download PDF Book Icon">
        </div>

        <div class="collation-details">
          <h2>Download The Pack</h2>
          <p>
            Downloading this pack will give you a PDF that you can look through with your patient to ensure that everything you feel
            they will need is there in the pack.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="collation-info">
          <p>
            This option allows you to go back to editing the pack if anything has been missed
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="collation-btnWrapper">
          <button class="icon-button ghost-btn download-pack">
            <i class="fa fa-cloud-download" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <span>Download</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Send for collation and despatch -->
      <div class="collation-table-cell">
        <div class="collation-icon">
          <img src="data:image/png;base64," width="86px" height="71px" alt="Send for Collation Icon">
        </div>

        <div class="collation-details">
          <h2>Send Pack For Collation And Despatch </h2>
          <p>
            If you feel you have finished the pack and you and your patient are happy you can now send the pack to be collated. Using
            these options will lockdown the pack options and prevent further editing.
          </p>
          <p>
            Pack includes pill packet labels, medication interaction card and the information personalised for your patient.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="collation-btnWrapper">
          <button class="icon-button download-pack">
            <i class="fa fa-paper-plane" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <span>Download and send for collation</span>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="collation-btnWrapper">
          <button class="icon-button download-pack" id="send-collation">
            <i class="fa fa-paper-plane" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <span>Send for collation</span>
          </button>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


